      <div type="translation" resp="part:argr">
         <p>In <supplied reason="explanation">the year of the</supplied> Śaka king 975. This was when his majesty Śrī Parameśvaravarmadeva repaired the deity Mañjuvara <supplied reason="explanation">i.e., Mañjuśrī</supplied>. He gave back personnel and all <foreign>sanaṅgūv</foreign> as in former times.</p>
       </div>
